reviewText: This was a movie I've been trying to find for quite some time but had a hard time finding a copy.  Nobody had it not Bestbuy, Walmart or even target. I even researched it on the web and still couldn't find a copy. Once I saw that there was a copy available on Amazon I jumped at the chance to get one. The copy was very poor quality. The picture for most of it was slightly blurry and out of focus. It was truly not worth the money I paid.
